cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.LG

The paper discusses the security of heterogeneous wireless sensor networks (HWSNET) and proposes a framework for intrusion detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as the paper deals with wireless sensor networks, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the proposed framework involves clustering, cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the paper discusses the impact of attacks on the system, and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the proposed framework involves a layered countermeasure.
